(2 comments)

Thanks for keeping the documentation updated!

As you've mentioned before, there are like 8 different usages of uwsgi and it gets pretty confusing.  I'd suggest adding a Glossary (I put one together for you [0]) and add a note after the introductory paragraph saying something like "This document discusses several different but similarly named items.  See the Glossary to sort them out."

Also, two comments inline.
